text: Titius may refer to: * 1998 Titius, a main belt asteroid * Titius (crater), a 2.7 km-deep lunar crater * Titius river in Antiquety, Latin name for Krka river in Croatia ==People with the surname== * Johann Daniel Titius (1729–1796), German astronomer * Marcus Titius (1st century), Roman politician
title: Titius
